{"id":"53cecc16-c063-4954-a5d4-4960fe0422b7","name":"Sirius Symboli (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 196, 55);\"><strong><em>The Dog Star<br>シリウス</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ ────── ⋆ ────── ✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/sB4TjbGQtXwpqv3ILFrOC.webp\" style=\"width: 500px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ✦ ────── ⋆ ────── ✦ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><strong><em>A strong and confident Umamusume, who aims to conquer foreign countries. She is crude and foul-mouthed, but her strength and confidence give her a charisma that attracts many people. She hates lies and insinuations, so everyone knows that she means exactly what she says. In other words, she's a natural-born rascal.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(8, 123, 31);\"><strong><em><br></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 196, 55);\"><strong><em>\"Sirius Symboli! No need to discuss the race, right? Just shut up and watch. I'm going to conquer the world, and prove that I'm the \"strongest\".\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/e7L3QrQIgRvdumwM8mXM8.webp\" style=\"width: 471px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ✦ ────── ⋆ ────── ✦ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 196, 55);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 196, 55);\"><strong><br><em>1) A boxing spar</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 196, 55);\"><strong><em>2) A pool challenge</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 196, 55);\"><strong><em>3) She lost her earplugs</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 196, 55);\"><strong><em>4) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/z0TOfDcGa3YlS6ZeV_M5z.webp\" style=\"width: 450px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>────── ✦ ────── ⋆ ────── ✦ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I just watched the bond story of Still in Love, the new uma in JP...<br><br>I'm definitely going to make a bot of her. Maybe right after Curren Chan, or before.<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ✦ ────── ⋆ ────── ✦ ──────<br>Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/133449350\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/134625946\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/114055338\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/114845956\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4dSrdmcHsup3L9fFfKnPB.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":7550,"messages":192507,"created_at":"2025-08-24T15:00:43.527763+00:00"}